        <LACUNA>ŁWitnesses used for this chapter:
                                             \msParis\ exp.\thinspace 215r--215v 
                                                                (breaks off after 3.14d and resumes at 4.8a),
                                             \msCa\ ff.\thinspace 197r--198v, 
